{"tid":177948,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"清潔工報假案稱有拐子婆","createTime":"2017-03-29T08:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T08:35:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"efe8cb34a689c6f2d807c470c910a20019db9d44","tid":177948,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T08:13:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19973269&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19973269%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170329&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnANZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=6e0ffe55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19973269%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170329&h=70f2f5e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19973269&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170329</a><br />\n<br />\n清潔工報假案稱有拐子婆<br />\n<br />\n法庭&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n九龍城法院<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】城市大學清潔男工稱因子女頑皮及工作壓力大，由新聞報道得知有人拐帶兒童後，撥999訛稱有拐子婆在商場騷擾他，又引誘其6歲兒子玩，更揚言其子能在內地賣得好價錢。警方翻看現場閉路電視，發現清潔工當日從未在商場出現。清潔工昨承認誤導警務人員罪，裁判官斥他會引起公眾恐慌，下月18日判刑。<br />\n38歲被告邱德基於上月8日報假案，訛稱有拐子婆在鳳德商場出現。他被警揭發後稱「因為我工作壓力大，又睇到拐帶兒童新聞後想學校更加關注」。辯方昨求情指被告愚蠢及錯誤犯案，他向校方反映有拐子婆，校方建議他報警。被告僱主求情信稱他盡責。主任裁判官羅德泉准他保釋候判。<br />\n案件編號：KCCC482/17<br />\n■記者伍嘉豪"},{"pid":"26228c49cd886ef10846928dff217563683cc21d","tid":177948,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T08:15:25.000Z","msg":"點解佢唔姓肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2457e007f8b28c3c1d58592fc6794b0a31967af6","tid":177948,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解佢唔姓肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj